===Verb===
'''קרא''' (qara')

# to [[read]], to [[call]]

[[fr:קרא]]
[[hu:קרא]]

{{HH|7121}} 
קרא / qârâ' / kaw-raw'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root (rather identical with H7122 through the idea of accosting a person met); 
=== Verb ===
to call out to (that is, properly address by name, but used in a wide variety of applications): - bewray [self], that are bidden, call (for, forth, self, upon), cry (unto), (be) famous, guest, invite, mention, (give) name, preach, (make) proclaim (-ation), pronounce, publish, read, renowned, say.